name: digiNERATES —> Dive Bar Dominic
description: In the bowels of your city’s grimiest watering hole there he is, body by booze, propped up on a rickety stool by a belly full of backwash bourbon and pilfered maraschino cherries. The only time he leaves his throne is to relieve himself at the commode and maybe, occasionally scrub his teeth with a mixture of hand soap and absinthe. He’s your friendly neighborhood waste of space.
